Where $D_c$ is

$$ D_c = \text{LCM}(D_1,D_2) $$

Comparing $n_1$ and $n_2$ will give us the result which fraction is bigger.


This method work because the ratio of $\frac{N_1}{D_1}$ $\frac{n_1}{D_c}$ will be same


